body:
Hey, recently i've been wondering of everyone who has left avicus. Since ive been playing since 2013 I've seen alot of people go whether they come back after two weeks or not i find it kind of emotional i guess... I was just wondering who you can remember that has left avicus?  

Its actually quite sad because i feel so bad as i cant remember many people.

Just comment anyone who you remember that has left Avicus, to bring back the memories of the good ol' days.
